commit.message:
fix(es/minifier): Disable inlining of expressions from `collapse_vars` (#3200)

swc_ecma_minifier:
 - `collapse_vars`: Disable for member expressions. (Closes #2614)
 - `sequences`: Respect `inline_prevented`.

fix(es/minifier): Drop unreachable statements eagerly (#3204)

swc_ecma_minifier:
 - `pure`: Drop unreachable statements. (Closes #3173)

feat(plugin): Pass serialized ast to a wasm file (#3199)

swc_common:
 - Use correct cargo feature for plugin apis.

swc_plugin:
 - Add hidden functions required for memory operations from host.

swc_plugin_runner:
 - Pass serialized AST to a wasm file.

feat(es/transforms): Add `Assumptions` (#3215)

swc_ecma_transforms_base:
 - Add `Assumptions`. (Closes #2057)

swc_ecma_transforms:
 - Reexport `Assumptions`.

swc:
 - Add `jsc.assumptions`.
refactor(es/compat): Preserve length of functions in `async_generator` (#3202)
feat(plugin): Allow multi-value for the plugin signature (#3216)
chore(es/minifier): Add scripts to extract tests automatically (#3212)
feat(plugin): Perform actual transforms in plugins (#3220)

refactor(es/ast): Change types of member-like expressions (#3178)

swc_ecma_ast:
 - Split `MemberExpr` into `MemberExpr` and `SuperPropExpr`.
 - Use `Box<Expr>` for `MemberExpr.obj`.
 - Use ad-hoc type for `MemberExpr.prop`.
 - Use ad-hoc type for `SuperPropExpr.prop`.
 - Use `Callee` instead of  `ExprOrSpread` for `CallExpr`.
 - Simplify types for meta property expressions.

feat(es/ast): Update `is-macro` (#3226)

swc_ecma_ast:
 - Add `as_*` for ast enums.

fix(es/modules): Fix lazy import handling (#3211)

swc_ecma_transforms_module:
 - `common_js`: Correctly track lazy imports. (Closes #3081)

feat(es/compat): Implement object super (#3127)

swc_ecma_transforms_compat:
 - Implement object super. (Closes #2684)

feat(plugin): Don't serialize/deserialize needlessly (#3227)

swc_common:
 - Add `Serialized`.

swc_plugin_runner:
 - Accept `Serialized` instead of `Program`.
 - Pass `Serialized` from previous plugin instead of deserializing it.
fix(es/minifier): Fix handling of inlined call to a hoisted function (#3223)
feat(plugin/macro): Add safe API for plugins based on a proc-macro (#3240)

fix(swc): Remove `wrong-target` (#3251)

swc:
 - Remove the cargo feature `wrong-target`. (Closes #1108)
build(node): Fix glibc issue on linux gnu arm (#3255)

fix(es/transforms): Fix `this` in async arrow class properties (#3252)

swc_ecma_transforms_compat:
 - `async_to_generator`: Fix `this` in async class properties. (https://github.com/vercel/next.js/issues/33283)
 - Add a test for #3228 (Closes #3228).

fix(es/minifier): Preserve side effects in correct position (#3263)

swc_ecma_minifier:
 - Add `fake_block` mark.
 - Inject statements for side effects from `visit_mut_stmt` instead of `visit_mut_stmt_likes`. (Closes #2926)
feat(es/compat): Use `var` for `_len` and `args` in rest parameters (#3267)
fix(es/resolver): Treat a switch statement as a block scope (#3275)

fix(es/react): Fix `createElement` (#3277)

swc_ecma_transforms_react:
 - Fix arguments passed to `_createElement`. (https://github.com/vercel/next.js/issues/33291)
fix(es/parser): Throw an error when function body has use strict and paramaters is not simple (#3278)

feat(es/ast): Improve AST api for plugin authors (#3281)

swc_ecma_ast:
 - Improve API for AST creation.
fix(es/transforms): Handle template literals within `jsonify` pass (#3282)
refactor(es/utils): Merge the super field visitor with `FnEnvHoister` (#3279)

fix(es/minifier): Fix analysis of unary expressions (#3286)

swc_ecma_minifier:
 - Mark update as usage and assignment. (Closes #3265)

fix(es/minifier): Inline into interpolations in tagged template literals (#3287)

swc_ecma_minifier:
 - Inline into tagged template literals. (Closes #2923)
feat(es/compat): Use remove useless source map entries generated by `classes` (#3242)

fix(es/resolver): Ignore names of jsx attributes (#3289)

swc_ecma_transforms_base:
 - Ignore names of jsx attributes. (Closes #2854)
fix(common): Use `siphasher` directly and upgrade transitive dependencies to avoid UB (#3299)

fix(es/minifier): Remove more side-effect-free expressions. (#3301)

swc_ecam_minifier:
- `pure`: Drop more binary expressions.
- `pure`: Drop more literals.

feat(es/minifier): Drop more expressions from parallel optimizer (#3303)

swc_ecma_minifier:
 - `pure`: Implement more rule for dropping useless expressions.

fix(es/minifier): Don't emit invalid code (#3302)

swc_ecma_minifier:
 - Add lots of debug assertions for invalid codes.
 - Remove all invalid AST nodes eagerly.
 - `pure`: Normalize `PatOrExpr`.
 - `analyzer`: Handle `PatOrExpr` correctly.
test(plugin/runner): Pin dependencies for the integration test (#3306)

fix(es/minifier): Fix logic for checking `arguments` (#3313)

swc_ecma_minifier:
 - Don't mark `arguments` in nested scope as a inline blocker.

fix(es/minifier): Prevent infinite loop due to negation (#3310)

swc_ecma_minifier:
 - Don't mark as modified while negating.
build(node-swc): Fix GLIBC < 2.18 compatible issues and android arm binary loading issue (#3314)

fix(css): Fix parsing of media queries (#3318)

Co-authored-by: Donny/강동윤 <kdy1997.dev@gmail.com>
fix(css/parser): Fix parsing of at rules (#3328)

fix(es/minifier): Consider capturing while inlining (#3322)

swc_ecma_minifier:
 - Don't inline functions if it captures the environment.

fix(es/minifier): Don't inline a var if the initializer is reassigned (#3333)

swc_ecma_minifier:
 - Consider reassignment to initializer while inlining a variable.
fix(es/typescript): Handle typescript enums with string values (#3339)
refactor(css/ast): Merge several kinds of blocks into a single type (#3336)

fix(es/minifier): Respect block scoping while negating if statements (#3344)

swc_ecma_minifier:
 - Don't negate a if statement if it has `let`/`const` binding.

feat(es/minifier): Handle array literals in `sequences` (#3348)

swc_ecma_minifier:
 - `sequences`: Implement more rules for array literals.

fix(swc): Respect `jsc.experimental.keepImportAssertions` (#3352)

swc:
 - Fix `Merge` impl of `JscExperimental`.
feat(css/ast): Add `Ratio`, which is defined by spec (#3335)
fix(es/loader): Add an option to resolve symlinks with `true` as a default (#3340)
feat(plugin): Pass host context to plugins for diagnostics emission (#3359)

fix(es/block-scoping): Pop scope correctly on early returns (#3360)

swc_ecma_transforms_compat:
 - `block_scoping`: Pop scope even on fast-path.
refactor(css/ast): Fix type definitions related to `@import` at-rule (#3351)

fix(es/minifier): Prepend/append correctly (#3367)

swc_ecma_minifier:
 - Add some assertions for injections.
 - Fix prepend/append logic of statements.
feat(css/ast): Add types for dashed identifiers and `@color-profile` at-rules (#3364)

feat(es/lints): Implement "no-console" rule (#3269)

swc_ecma_lints:
 - Add types for general configuration.
 - Add `no-console`rule.

swc:
 - Expose the lint config via `jsc.lints`.

fix(es/minifier): Improve minifier (#3350)

swc_ecma_transforms_optimization:
 - `expr_simplifier`: Track more changes.

swc_ecma_minifier:
 - Analyze after applying the pure optimizer.
 - Preserve access to a variable not in scope.
 - `compress`: Remove string literal if it was not a directive.
 - `pure/collapse_vars`: Merge vars declared in the first statement into one with initializers if `collapse_vars` and `join_vars` are enabled.
 - `unused`: Use `usage_count` instead of `ref_count`.
 - `unused`: Fix dropping rule for member expressions.
 - `unused`: Fix dropping rule for declarations.
 - `hoist_props`: Preserve exported items.
refactor(es/minifier): Merge execution tests into a file to make `git` faster (#3377)

perf(node-swc): Speed up `parse` and `parseFile` (#3380)

node-swc:
 - Use a worker thread for json serialization.
chore(repo): Add `clippy` to git push hook (#3383)
fix(es/compat): Add the missing span in `optional_chaining` (#3384)

feat(es/minifier): Implement `drop_console` (#3392)

swc_ecma_minifier:
 - Merge `drop_console` into pure optimizer.
 - Implement `drop_console`. (Closes #2321)
refactor(es/parser): Flatten tests to make `git` faster (#3393)

fix(swc): Run `resolver` before everything (#3400)

swc:
 - Use `ts_resolver` for typescript. This is required to handle decorators properly.
 - Apply `resolver` before creating custom passes.
fix(css/parser): Fix parser logic related to case insensivity (#3382)
feat(css/parser): Improve parsing of math functions (#3415)

feat(css): Improve codegen where `minify: true` (#3414)

swc_css_codegen:
 - Improve minification.

swc_css_parser:
 - Add parsing rule for `sum`.

fix(es/modules): Fix span of imports (#3418)

swc_ecma_transforms_module:
 - `common_js`: Use original span with the syntax conext of an import specifier.

feat(es/lints): Add `no-alert` and a feature gate (#3394)

swc_ecma_lints:
 - Implement `no-alert`
 - Add a feature gate for non-critical rules.
test(css/codegen): Verify AST is not broken after minification (#3430)
feat(css/lexer): Implement error recovery for functions (#3445)
feat(css/ast): Improve types related to `url` tokens (#3444)
feat(es/parser): Add an option to allow `super` outside of class methods (#3427)

fix(es/resolver): Fix handling of for statements (#3446)

swc_ecma_transforms_base:
 - `resolver`: Visit the body of a for statement in a nested visitor.

fix(es/parser): Fix parsing of decorators (#3449)

swc_ecma_parser:
 - Parse decorators using `parse_subscripts`.
feat(css/codegen): Implement minification of hex colors (#3453)
test(css/parser): Add more tests for the selector parser (#3455)
fix(es/fixer): Handle more expressions in the super class position (#3452)
refactor(css/ast): Refactor types related to selectors (#3460)

fix(es/minifier): Fix `mapbox` (#3463)

swc_ecma_minifier:
 - `mangler`: Handle the identifiers of class expressions correctly.
feat(es/lints): Implement linter for quotes of string literals (#3443)
